','Prop_Unsafe','Total Acres Burned']].head())\n\n# final rounded\nprint(round(corr,2))", "dataset_id": "kramabench-wildfire-hard-14", "file_path": "files/annual_aqi_by_county_2024.csv"}) [toolUseId=call_U1IryMhkkq8qHfq5BgBAA1e8]
